Happy Match Privacy Policy
Effective Date:
2024-08-20
Welcome to Happy Match, your go-to casual puzzle game for a fun and engaging gaming experience. This Privacy Policy ("Policy") outlines our commitment to protecting your privacy while you enjoy our game.
1. Information We Do Not Collect
At Happy Match, we are dedicated to providing a gaming environment that respects your privacy. We do not collect any personal information from our players. Specifically, we do not gather the following:
Personal identifiers, such as real names, usernames, or contact information.
Device data, including device IDs, IP addresses, or location information.
Usage data, such as gameplay statistics or analytics.
2. Game Functionality
Happy Match is designed to be a standalone application that operates without the need for internet connectivity or user accounts. You can play the game without registering or providing any personal details.
3. Third-Party Services
Since we do not collect personal information, there is no sharing of data with third-party service providers or advertisers. Our game is self-sufficient and does not rely on external data processing.
4. Children's Privacy
Happy Match is intended for a general audience and is particularly suitable for players of all ages. We are committed to the privacy of children and, as we do not collect any information, we are in compliance with children's online privacy protection principles.
5. Data Security
Although we do not collect personal information, we understand the importance of data security. Our game is built with robust security measures to ensure the integrity of the game itself.
6. Policy Updates
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our privacy practices or in response to changes in privacy laws and regulations.
7. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please feel free to contact us. Our team is ready to assist you.
